WEBVTT

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:24.359
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.979
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.019
♪You're always♪

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:32.679
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.299
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.019
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:42.879
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:47.400
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 5=

00:00:55.780 --> 00:00:56.890
It's getting late.

00:01:02.250 --> 00:01:04.329
Do you have some kind of secret?

00:01:04.330 --> 00:01:05.010
Hold on.

00:01:21.330 --> 00:01:22.530
What are you doing?

00:01:23.180 --> 00:01:24.249
You're being so nice to me today.

00:01:24.250 --> 00:01:25.849
Is it because
I've saved you so many times

00:01:25.850 --> 00:01:27.570
that you want to marry me
to repay the favor?

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:29.989
♪If longing can be folded♪

00:01:29.990 --> 00:01:33.799
♪It would return to yesterday
with the proper stamp♪

00:01:33.800 --> 00:01:39.109
♪Where is the edge of the dream?♪

00:01:39.110 --> 00:01:42.659
♪Always measuring the interval
between breath and silence♪

00:01:42.660 --> 00:01:45.999
♪Like fishing
for raindrops in the desert♪

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:50.210
♪If time stopped spinning♪

00:01:50.750 --> 00:01:53.509
♪Our passion would expire♪

00:01:53.510 --> 00:01:56.979
♪If my heart refuses
to compromise with the night♪

00:01:56.980 --> 00:01:59.659
♪I'll tear out my ribs
to strike the stars louder♪

00:01:59.660 --> 00:02:00.779
(He Min)

00:02:00.780 --> 00:02:03.930
♪Settling in my veins♪

00:02:06.020 --> 00:02:07.409
Applying some medicine

00:02:07.410 --> 00:02:09.020
means marrying to repay the favor?

00:02:09.140 --> 00:02:11.740
Captain Shen,
you're being a bit too conceited.

00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:31.850
Are you sure
my dad is in this nursing home?

00:02:31.930 --> 00:02:34.580
Based on the logo
on the stationery you gave me, I'm sure.

00:02:34.810 --> 00:02:35.810
There's no mistake.

00:02:47.580 --> 00:02:48.979
I'll go distract them in a moment.

00:02:48.980 --> 00:02:50.500
You take the chance
to get into the ward.

00:03:03.580 --> 00:03:04.340
Who's there?

00:03:32.930 --> 00:03:33.769
What are you doing?

00:03:33.770 --> 00:03:36.740
Who let you in? Can you take responsibility
for disturbing the patient?

00:03:43.420 --> 00:03:45.300
(Oh no, my dad has been moved.)

00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:47.930
Honey,

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:49.459
didn't I tell you?

00:03:49.460 --> 00:03:51.460
Dad is in the room next door, not here.

00:03:51.860 --> 00:03:52.979
Sorry about that, gentlemen.

00:03:52.980 --> 00:03:53.979
We've got the wrong place.

00:03:53.980 --> 00:03:55.020
We're leaving now.

00:04:16.730 --> 00:04:17.820
Shen Jibai,

00:04:17.900 --> 00:04:19.530
why are you here?

00:04:20.500 --> 00:04:22.579
Don't tell me
this is another coincidence.

00:04:22.580 --> 00:04:23.960
Of course it's not a coincidence.

00:04:24.410 --> 00:04:25.340
What?

00:04:26.090 --> 00:04:27.610
A suspicious person?

00:04:29.090 --> 00:04:30.729
I don't care what means you use,

00:04:30.730 --> 00:04:33.140
move that old man
out of here immediately.

00:04:34.770 --> 00:04:36.050
If you run into anyone in the way,

00:04:36.170 --> 00:04:38.340
teach them a lesson.

00:04:40.820 --> 00:04:42.289
I'm your personal bodyguard.

00:04:42.290 --> 00:04:44.580
Isn't it normal
for me to be here with you?

00:04:45.410 --> 00:04:46.969
Otherwise, in that situation just now,

00:04:46.970 --> 00:04:48.329
Miss Mu, how would you have handled it?

00:04:48.330 --> 00:04:49.490
Shen Jibai,

00:04:49.850 --> 00:04:51.850
you don't think
I still believe you, do you?

00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:55.260
So much has happened over the past month,
and you've been there every single time.

00:04:56.060 --> 00:04:57.380
Don't you find it strange?

00:04:57.460 --> 00:04:58.410
Yu.

00:05:02.770 --> 00:05:03.409
How is it?

00:05:03.410 --> 00:05:04.380
Did you find him?

00:05:04.500 --> 00:05:05.580
I didn't find my dad.

00:05:06.530 --> 00:05:08.730
It seems they
got word of this ahead of time.

00:05:09.330 --> 00:05:10.089
There they are!

00:05:10.090 --> 00:05:10.409
Stop!

00:05:10.410 --> 00:05:10.969
Yu,

00:05:10.970 --> 00:05:11.409
let's go.

00:05:11.410 --> 00:05:12.050
Don't run!

00:05:12.210 --> 00:05:13.020
Stop right there!

00:05:20.060 --> 00:05:22.410
I've been
the Business Director for a while now.

00:05:22.530 --> 00:05:24.940
When can I report
my work to the Chairman?

00:05:30.530 --> 00:05:31.940
I've already told you.

00:05:31.970 --> 00:05:33.899
Your dad doesn't want
to see anyone right now.

00:05:33.900 --> 00:05:35.580
He just wants to rest well.

00:05:35.770 --> 00:05:37.020
I want to know,

00:05:37.330 --> 00:05:38.940
is this my dad's wish,

00:05:39.170 --> 00:05:40.490
or yours?

00:05:41.580 --> 00:05:42.490
Zhiyu,

00:05:42.650 --> 00:05:45.090
I understand
your concern for your father,

00:05:45.380 --> 00:05:46.580
but

00:05:46.650 --> 00:05:48.530
you know your dad's personality.

00:05:49.020 --> 00:05:49.970
Don't worry.

00:05:50.260 --> 00:05:51.730
He will show up

00:05:52.020 --> 00:05:53.340
at the exhibition in three days.

00:05:54.530 --> 00:05:55.379
Also,

00:05:55.380 --> 00:05:56.619
if I were you,

00:05:56.620 --> 00:05:58.059
what I'd be more worried about

00:05:58.060 --> 00:05:59.819
is the stolen exhibit.

00:05:59.820 --> 00:06:01.089
If, in three days,

00:06:01.090 --> 00:06:04.410
you can't produce
a heavy-hitting centerpiece,

00:06:05.290 --> 00:06:07.280
the directors
will be dissatisfied with you,

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:08.970
and I won't be able to protect you.

00:06:11.700 --> 00:06:12.619
Thank you

00:06:12.620 --> 00:06:15.340
(Three days later)
for joining Mu Group's exhibition today.

00:06:15.530 --> 00:06:16.819
Before the exhibition begins,

00:06:16.820 --> 00:06:18.650
please watch a short video.

00:06:20.730 --> 00:06:21.769
Welcome, everyone,

00:06:21.770 --> 00:06:24.499
to the annual Mu Group exhibition.

00:06:24.500 --> 00:06:25.610
(Dad...)

00:06:25.700 --> 00:06:27.169
Due to health reasons,

00:06:27.170 --> 00:06:28.459
I am unable to attend.

00:06:28.460 --> 00:06:30.580
I deeply regret this.

00:06:31.460 --> 00:06:34.850
Mu Group is currently
at a critical stage.

00:06:35.380 --> 00:06:37.089
My only daughter, Mu Zhiyu,

00:06:37.090 --> 00:06:38.409
is still young

00:06:38.410 --> 00:06:40.260
and lacks both ability and experience.

00:06:41.020 --> 00:06:42.490
But fortunately,

00:06:43.020 --> 00:06:44.579
I have a wife as capable

00:06:44.580 --> 00:06:46.530
and efficient as Mingzhu.

00:06:46.730 --> 00:06:48.899
I am very confident
in leaving the company

00:06:48.900 --> 00:06:50.050
in her hands.

00:06:50.770 --> 00:06:53.020
For the foreseeable future,

00:06:53.170 --> 00:06:54.209
I hope

00:06:54.210 --> 00:06:56.650
she can continue
to preside over company affairs

00:06:57.260 --> 00:06:59.290
and lead our Mu Group

00:06:59.410 --> 00:07:00.289
toward

00:07:00.290 --> 00:07:01.820
a better future.

00:07:07.900 --> 00:07:08.769
I believe you all

00:07:08.770 --> 00:07:10.729
have felt the Chairman's sincerity.

00:07:10.730 --> 00:07:12.780
I hope you all enjoy yourselves today.

00:07:13.530 --> 00:07:14.499
But

00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:16.059
I have one more thing

00:07:16.060 --> 00:07:17.380
to tell everyone.

00:07:18.170 --> 00:07:19.329
Regrettably,

00:07:19.330 --> 00:07:21.050
- we...
- What Ms. Xu means is,

00:07:23.140 --> 00:07:26.220
there were indeed
some minor hiccups with this exhibition.

00:07:26.380 --> 00:07:27.289
However,

00:07:27.290 --> 00:07:28.409
it is only with surprises

00:07:28.410 --> 00:07:29.650
that there can be breakthroughs.

00:07:30.290 --> 00:07:31.460
Next,

00:07:31.580 --> 00:07:33.259
allow me to introduce

00:07:33.260 --> 00:07:35.410
the centerpiece of this exhibition.

00:07:45.650 --> 00:07:47.290
(Could it be...)

00:07:48.650 --> 00:07:50.730
The centerpiece of this exhibition,

00:07:54.260 --> 00:07:55.619
the Han Dynasty White Jade Bowl.

00:07:55.620 --> 00:07:56.730
Please, take a look.

00:07:58.580 --> 00:08:00.090
(How is this possible?)

00:08:00.580 --> 00:08:01.729
(I guessed right.)

00:08:01.730 --> 00:08:04.020
(Mu Zhiyu really isn't simple.)

00:08:05.090 --> 00:08:06.169
I heard somewhere

00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:07.970
that Mu Group had been robbed.

00:08:08.060 --> 00:08:09.499
This Han Dynasty White Jade Bowl

00:08:09.500 --> 00:08:10.289
was supposedly

00:08:10.290 --> 00:08:11.619
lost.

00:08:11.620 --> 00:08:12.580
Is that for real?

00:08:12.970 --> 00:08:13.899
This exhibit is...

00:08:13.900 --> 00:08:15.699
This Western Han Plain Jade Bowl

00:08:15.700 --> 00:08:17.899
has a dignified and elegant form,

00:08:17.900 --> 00:08:18.649
and it's unadorned

00:08:18.650 --> 00:08:20.020
yet exquisitely crafted.

00:08:20.580 --> 00:08:22.260
Please look at its rim.

00:08:22.260 --> 00:08:24.050
The body of the bowl
curves slightly outward.

00:08:24.460 --> 00:08:25.849
And look at its inner wall.

00:08:25.850 --> 00:08:27.380
The luster is delicate.

00:08:27.410 --> 00:08:28.490
As the ancients said...

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:30.410
(This little brat...)

00:08:30.460 --> 00:08:32.220
(I underestimated her.)

00:08:32.410 --> 00:08:34.010
It's an honor

00:08:34.100 --> 00:08:34.979
to have

00:08:34.980 --> 00:08:36.259
this jade bowl

00:08:36.260 --> 00:08:38.890
included in the Mu Group's exhibition.

00:08:38.900 --> 00:08:39.820
That's right.

00:08:40.260 --> 00:08:41.099
This jade bowl

00:08:41.100 --> 00:08:43.820
was acquired by my husband,
Mu Chenzhou, years ago.

00:08:43.900 --> 00:08:45.340
He is currently recuperating,

00:08:45.530 --> 00:08:46.979
but seeing his collection

00:08:46.980 --> 00:08:48.649
presented to everyone
through his daughter,

00:08:48.650 --> 00:08:50.770
Zhiyu's hands,

00:08:50.900 --> 00:08:52.370
is truly heartening.

00:08:52.410 --> 00:08:54.660
I also hope that in the future,

00:08:55.170 --> 00:08:56.809
Zhiyu will be able to achieve

00:08:56.810 --> 00:08:58.730
even better results for Mu Group.

00:09:01.220 --> 00:09:03.289
(I thought the theft
of the White Jade Bowl)

00:09:03.290 --> 00:09:05.700
(could get Mu Zhiyu
kicked out of the company.)

00:09:06.170 --> 00:09:08.580
(Who knew
she would actually find the bowl?)

00:09:11.530 --> 00:09:13.300
(It seems I need to speed up the plan.)

00:09:24.100 --> 00:09:26.490
I didn't expect you
to really find this White Jade Bowl.

00:09:27.860 --> 00:09:28.970
However,

00:09:29.220 --> 00:09:30.850
it wasn't my credit alone.

00:09:31.380 --> 00:09:33.920
If you hadn't reminded me,
I probably wouldn't have thought of it.

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:34.890
Me?

00:09:37.630 --> 00:09:38.619
- You must be careful.
- Okay.

00:09:38.620 --> 00:09:38.929
Right.

00:09:38.930 --> 00:09:40.180
- Check over here.
- Understood.

00:09:46.140 --> 00:09:48.090
(Xu Mingzhu loves money more than life.)

00:09:48.220 --> 00:09:50.770
(She would never
put a collection in a dangerous place.)

00:09:51.740 --> 00:09:54.490
(The police had already
sealed off the collection room.)

00:09:54.860 --> 00:09:57.250
(She wouldn't have had
a chance to take it out.)

00:09:57.740 --> 00:09:59.940
(The White Jade Bowl
had to still be inside.)

00:10:17.220 --> 00:10:18.420
If you put it that way,

00:10:18.690 --> 00:10:20.700
then the credit is entirely mine.

00:10:21.050 --> 00:10:21.979
You should thank me.

00:10:21.980 --> 00:10:23.420
Oh, thank you so much.

00:10:24.530 --> 00:10:26.940
I've never seen anyone
thicker-skinned than you.

00:10:27.650 --> 00:10:28.660
You're welcome.

00:10:32.100 --> 00:10:33.250
Don't worry.

00:10:33.530 --> 00:10:34.859
Regarding the nursing home,

00:10:34.860 --> 00:10:36.700
I will investigate thoroughly.

00:10:37.100 --> 00:10:40.060
Even if Xu Mingzhu hides
my dad at the edge of the world,

00:10:40.450 --> 00:10:42.180
I will definitely find him.

00:10:42.260 --> 00:10:44.370
I really didn't know
about the nursing home.

00:10:44.900 --> 00:10:46.250
The mission I was given

00:10:46.260 --> 00:10:47.739
was only to protect your safety.

00:10:47.740 --> 00:10:48.660
Is that so?

00:10:51.100 --> 00:10:52.339
Whether you knew it or not,

00:10:52.340 --> 00:10:53.739
since you've saved me a few times,

00:10:53.740 --> 00:10:55.300
I'll give you a friendly warning.

00:10:55.570 --> 00:10:57.649
Xu Mingzhu is no saint.

00:10:57.650 --> 00:10:59.090
If you work for her,

00:11:00.100 --> 00:11:01.940
be careful,
or you'll end up with nothing.

00:11:18.230 --> 00:11:22.460
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:26.969
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:11:26.970 --> 00:11:31.460
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:39.940
♪Shadows move around♪

00:11:40.030 --> 00:11:44.229
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:11:44.230 --> 00:11:48.760
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:11:52.360 --> 00:11:58.150
♪Don't slip away♪

00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:05.169
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:05.170 --> 00:12:09.569
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:09.570 --> 00:12:13.890
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:13.910 --> 00:12:17.890
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:18.360 --> 00:12:22.669
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:22.670 --> 00:12:26.999
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:31.309
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:31.310 --> 00:12:37.460
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪